### Health check
GET http://localhost:3333/health

### List clients (opcional: ?search=nome)
GET http://localhost:3333/clients

### Create client
POST http://localhost:3333/clients
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nome": "Cliente Exemplo",
    "email": "cliente@exemplo.com",
    "telefone": "11999999999",
    "documento": "12345678900",
    "ativo": true
}

### Get client by id (substitua :id)
GET http://localhost:3333/clients/8a9a9ee1-5306-4a23-a76d-6e334cfbe071

### Update client
PUT http://localhost:3333/clients/8a9a9ee1-5306-4a23-a76d-6e334cfbe071
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nome": "Cliente Atualizado",
    "email": "cliente.atualizado@exemplo.com",
    "telefone": "11988888888",
    "documento": "12345678900",
    "ativo": true
}

### Delete client
DELETE http://localhost:3333/clients/8a9a9ee1-5306-4a23-a76d-6e334cfbe071
